WEBVTT

00:01.238 --> 00:08.365
...test facing any captain, any crew, is the loss of a shipmate.

00:08.365 --> 00:11.835
We've come here to honor one of our own.

00:11.835 --> 00:17.983
In the time we knew him, he showed us just how much one life can truly matter.

00:17.983 --> 00:23.662
We will never forget what he did for us and for the ship he loved so much.

00:23.662 --> 00:27.947
We will go forward with renewed determination to complete this mission,

00:27.947 --> 00:33.243
so that his sacrifice won't just have been for the people on this ship,

00:33.243 --> 00:36.164
but for all the citizens of Earth.

00:40.827 --> 00:45.223
It's been a long road

00:45.223 --> 00:48.409
Getting from there to here

00:48.409 --> 00:52.349
It's been a long time

00:52.349 --> 00:56.267
But my time is finally near

00:56.267 --> 01:00.484
And I will see my dream come alive at last

01:00.484 --> 01:04.183
I will touch the sky

01:04.183 --> 01:07.843
And they're not gonna hold me down no more

01:07.843 --> 01:11.091
No, they're not gonna change my mind

01:11.091 --> 01:15.786
'Cause I've got faith of the heart

01:15.786 --> 01:18.710
I'm going where the heart will take me

01:18.710 --> 01:23.764
I've got faith to believe

01:23.764 --> 01:26.480
I can do anything

01:26.480 --> 01:31.283
I've got strength of the soul

01:31.283 --> 01:34.254
No one's gonna bend or break me

01:34.254 --> 01:40.159
I can reach any star

01:40.159 --> 01:43.861
I've got faith

01:43.861 --> 01:47.915
I've got faith

01:47.915 --> 01:50.831
Faith of the heart

